window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I know her as the unconscious girl I found bleeding out on the locker room floor.</b></p> <p>I got her help. I saved her life.</p> <p>The next time I see her, she makes it clear she wants nothing to do with me.</p> <p>Too bad. I didn't go through the trouble of saving her life just for her to throw it away again.</p> <p>She doesn't know it yet but I'm about to be her new best friend.</p> <p>The Savage <i>contains found family, trauma bonding, who-did-this-to-you vibes, a protective hero, he falls first, parental issues, and sports romance. Intended for mature listeners.</i></p>"; 
